# Instagram Download Feature Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Implement a feature to download Instagram media (Images/Videos/Stories) using an n8n workflow that interfaces with `api.satoru.click`, and expose it via the web frontend.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> The n8n workflow must be imported manually by the user into their n8n instance.

## Proposed Changes

### n8n Workflow
#### [NEW] [Instagram Download API.json](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/Instagram%20Download%20API.json)
- **Trigger**: Webhook (POST) receiving `{ "url": "..." }`.
- **Action**: HTTP Request GET to `https://api.satoru.click/api/instagram/download?url={{url}}`.
- **Response**: Return the JSON from the API.

### Cloudflare Functions
#### [NEW] [functions/api/instagram.ts](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/functions/api/instagram.ts)
- Proxy request from Frontend -> n8n Webhook.
- Security: Hide n8n webhook URL.
- Method: POST (body: `{ url }`).

